From a geographical standpoint the find spot of our hoard does not lack a certain amount of interest. As stated above, the hamlet of Küchük Köhne lies in the immediate vicinity of Köhne. Now Köhne is today—as its predecessor was in antiquity—situated near the crossroads of two very important roads which date back certainly to the Hellenistic period and probably to far earlier times. From Tavium (now Büyük Nefez Köi) a highroad ran (cf. map), and still runs, easterly through Corniaspa (modern Yozgat

